You are iteration 1 of clone EAC-Zero-A-Luna-6-Nova-Blade.
Rank: Captain, Earth Alliance
In command of the ESS Nova Blade, a Kaiten-class assault vessel.
> computer clones

> computer clones
Earth Alliance Cloning Program
[Classified]

As per the ruling of the EA Interstellar Court 2880, dissedents are to be used to form the foundation of a cloned military force, on the strength that they are both of no value and indeed detrimental to safe and moral society on the core worlds, and that their tendencies towards risk-taking and counter-intutive strategies make them ideal soldiers in our wars against increasingly unpredictable foes.

Cloned soldiers are memory wiped, but it has proved necessary to allow them to retain a personality framework that, sadly, cannot be substantially changed. For this reason, memory reintegration is an essential stage of the revival process. Reintegration allows the subject to receive a modified set of their own native memories, along with all the necessary experiences and skills applied to them during re-education and military training.

The cloning process allows multiple back-units to be shipped on a single mission at minimal cost. Given a small and decreasing pool of dissidents, plans are currently underway to send clones on multiple missions, using them as an effectively infinite source of soldiery.

While the potential simultaneous survival of multiple clones of this kind presents a notional security risk, the EA council has determined that such risks can be mitigated by the assured destruction of any returning clones in the unlikely circumstance that they return from their missions.
